Information
------------------------------
Caribbean breeze.

The Caribbean evokes our desire to travel, somewhere between the lagoons and fertile volcanic islands. The collective imagination clings to this image of an island paradise, like the one discovered by the early explorers, or pirate treasure hidden deep beneath the white sands. A postcard of the Caribbean?
